# MOD-JS: Shared Logic + Data + Adapter (TypeScript)

- **Write:** `sidecar-app/src/services/` ONLY (e.g., `SideCarAdapter.ts`, utility modules)
- **Read:** All `sidecar-app/src/**/*.tsx` component files
- **Focus:** INTEGRATIONS.md, SECURITY.md, DEVELOPMENT.md
- **Key Constraints:** C-01, C-02, C-03, C-09, C-10

Contains SideCarAdapter TypeScript interface, synthetic data, utility functions, PRD computation.
- No fetch() (C-02)
- TypeScript ES module imports/exports are used (Vite bundled)
- All data synthetic with defined patterns (C-03)
- Adapter interface contract must not change without Tier 1 authorization (C-09)
- Comm log is append-only (C-10)
- PRD computation is LOCKED — tier thresholds require Tier 1 to modify
Do NOT modify any `.tsx` component files or `sidecar-app/src/index.css` from this module.
